{"tid":1548422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「林鄭批中」【政情號外】831終局之戰未達緊急情況　林鄭暫緩硬招轉用懷柔","createTime":"2019-09-07T04:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T04:14:17.000Z","uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad730cdf1988f5dddb14abe883401a528f84717f","tid":1548422,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"《政情》四出打聽由硬變軟的轉捩點是剛過去的周末，民陣831五周年遊行被拒，網上一片「終局之戰」討論下，政府和建制原先評估示威暴力行動進一步升級，擔心警民衝突下出現傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n多於一名消息人士向《政情》透露，政府內部已擬備緊急法內容，是否引用831的情況成關鍵。民陣遊行申請被拒下，831仍有大量市民上街遊行至下午已開始有衝突，示威者投擲汽油彈，警方出動水炮車亦首用顏色水，但整體衝突中未有政府及建制原先預期的「激烈」，內部評估暫未需要引用緊急法，反而順勢推軟招緩和局面。"},{"pid":"5e8c05fe4b396577c21f2459fab1679db538f717","tid":1548422,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 終極文宣 對準政權 全民抗共</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}